ygData.messageBody:
I just dinged 37 and this is my equipment. I
moved my character from the Brell server to the
Casic-Thule server and my guild decked me out pretty well.

the dead mobs or quest items.<br>Equipment<br><br>Orc

Electrum Bracelet<br>Bracer of Scavenging<br>Mithril
Vambraces<br>Darkmail Gauntlets<br>Blood Stained Mantle<br>Tree
Weave<br>Dire Wolf Fur Cloak<br>Crystalline Belt<br>Mithril
Greaves<br>Dwarven Work Boots<br>Ykeshan War Club<br>Stormfeather
